MERN STACK
M = mongo db used as a database
E = express JS used for api backend
R = React JS   used for developing frontend
N = Node js used for backend

Roles of each technologies
1 Mongodb -> database which is a nosql database.There are Libraries in Mongodb.
2 Expressjs -> APIs used to create APIs and it is a backend part.
3 React JS -> JS Library used to make UI.
4 NodeJS - Bakend JS-> server

HTML: creates the structuree of webpage.
CSS : Used for design, and apperance layout of the webpage.
Javscript: To make dynamic and interactive websites.
Inside the head part there are meta components and inside the body it contains of the main details.
  
